```json
{
  "application": "SLURM",
  "details": {
    "job_name": "mesh_nbody_benchmark",
    "partition": "gpu_p2",
    "ntasks": 4,
    "nodes": 1,
    "ntasks_per_node": 4,
    "gres": "gpu:4",
    "cpus_per_task": 10,
    "hint": "nomultithread",
    "time": "00:15:00",
    "output": "mesh_nbody_benchmark_%j.out",
    "error": "mesh_nbody_benchmark_%j.out",
    "account": "ftb@gpu",
    "mail_user": "denise.lanzieri@cea.fr",
    "qos": "qos_gpu-dev",
    "modules": [
      "tensorflow-gpu/py3/2.4.1+cuda-11.2",
      "nvidia-nsight-systems/2021.1.1"
    ],
    "environment_variables": {
      "TMPDIR": "$JOBSCRATCH"
    },
    "commands": [
      "ln -s $JOBSCRATCH /tmp/nvidia",
      "srun --unbuffered --mpi=pmi2 -o mesh_nbody_%t.log /gpfslocalsup/pub/idrtools/bind_gpu.sh nsys profile --stats=true -t nvtx,cuda,mpi -o result-%q{SLURM_TASK_PID} python -u mesh_nbody_benchmark.py  --nc=128 --batch_size=1 --nx=2 --ny=2 --hsize=32 --nsteps=3"
    ],
    "code": "mesh_nbody_benchmark.py",
    "dependencies": {
      "libraries": [
        "tensorflow-gpu",
        "nvidia-nsight-systems",
        "mpi"
      ],
      "tools": [
        "nsys",
        "python",
        "bind_gpu.sh"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```
